nsor schemes, modes of collecting data, archiving, and data distribution at ONC, the workflow tool ensures that infrastructure is managed completely from instrument purchase to data distribution. It integrates all areas of expertise and helps fulfill ONC’s mandate to offer quality data to users.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/85062", "section":"Earth and Space Science Informatics"} 
