tly by evapotranspiration, has been remarkably similar across a period of changing land cover, leaving a relatively consistent proportion for groundwater recharge and streamflow.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/85161", "section":"Hydrology"} 
