positions are likely responsible for differences in B concentrations. Enami et al., J. Metamorphic Geol., 22, 1-15 (2004). Miyamoto et al., J. of Min. and Petro. Sci., 102, 352-367 (2007)", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/85219", "section":"Volcanology"} 
