y of rock matrices and different granitoids in the SNB isotopic trends can be evaluated to determine if crystals sizes are dependent on disequilibrium processes or grow at a steady state.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/85728", "section":"Volcanology"} 
