 While difference in δ15N of ecosystem components between sites is consistent with global trends, the absolute values for the whole study area are relatively low and attributed to N inputs from industrial sources depleted in 15N.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/85820", "section":"Biogeosciences"} 
