ented, to serve as potential reference and guidance for other projects seeking to grow their own communities. In addition, we will discuss how the Office’s role in outreach and engagement has changed over the past year with the creation of the Engagement and Liaison Teams, and what it signifies for the Office’s role in EarthCube’s future.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/86039", "section":"Earth and Space Science Informatics"} 
