 bacterial species (symbiotic or non-symbiotic) are described within a dynamic energy budget framework. The model offers a mechanistic framework to predict the optimal microalgal community assemblage towards high productivity and resistance to invasion under prevailing environmental conditions.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/86062", "section":"Biogeosciences"} 
