n eroding banks may be correlated to riffle location. In addition, bulk sampling in recently exposed reservoir deposits allows us to estimate the gravel and cobble fractions of the pulse of sediment released to the downstream river after the final portion of Glines Canyon Dam was removed in August 2014.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/86111", "section":"Earth and Planetary Surface Processes"} 
