wer plants and watersheds as well as the level of potential reduction of electricity generation under various drought scenarios and provide valuable insights into future mitigation strategies and long-term planning.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/86233", "section":"Global Environment Change"} 
