 to ensure that MCSDSS is searchable and clearly described.   MCSDSS is a flexible platform that allows for data fusion and inclusion of large datasets in an interactive front-end application capable of connecting with other science-based applications and advanced computing resources. In addition, MCSDSS offers functionality that enables communication with non-technical users for policy, education, or engagement with groups around scientific topics with societal relevance.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/86234", "section":"Earth and Space Science Informatics"} 
