 stochastic. Granger causality analysis between EVI2 and possible response variables indicates which variables (and with what lags) are to be included in DFA, resulting in unique Dynamic Factor Models for each cluster.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/86254", "section":"Biogeosciences"} 
