 conducted and results compared will be compared among different setups. Moreover, we will measure adverse impacts of CNTs on the metabolic activities of M. vanbaalenii PYR-1, particularly its biodegradation of polycyclic aromatic hydrocarbons.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/86671", "section":"Hydrology"} 
