c range, and significantly improved spectral and spatial resolutions for the imager, for deployment on larger platforms such as Small Explorer missions.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/86705", "section":"Solar and Heliospheric Physics"} 
