 GPCP (Global Precipitation Climatology Project) dataset. The potential vorticity structure and evolution of composite extratropical cyclones is then compared in HiGEM and ERA-Interim, with starkly divergent results, which are related to differences in latent heating.", "url":"https://agu.confex.com/agu/fm15/meetingapp.cgi/Paper/86793", "section":"Atmospheric Sciences"} 
